OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a mostly dry, bright and
OL,6,Fbreezy start, some showery rain will
OL,7,Fmove across the region from the west
OL,8,Fduring Easter Sunday morning. Showers
OL,9,Fwill become isolated into the
OL,10,Fafternoon, with plenty of sunny spells
OL,11,Fdeveloping. A colder day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAn isolated light shower is
OL,14,Fpossible early this evening, but with
OL,15,Fa ridge of high pressure toppling
OL,16,Facross overnight it looks largely dry
OL,17,Fwith clear periods. A slight frost
OL,18,Fforming.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
